  stimulus_text = 'The debate over the proper use of artificial intelligence in the classroom is a nuanced one, with many different perspectives on the topic. Some educators believe that AI can be a valuable tool for personalizing education and providing students with individualized learning experiences. Others argue that AI systems can perpetuate bias and inequity, and that they may not adequately address the needs of all students. The debate is further complicated by concerns about the ethical implications of using AI in education, and by questions about how best to ensure that AI systems are used responsibly and ethically. What is the most likely reason why the writer uses the word "complicated"?',
