  stimulus_text = 'A study of college students found that students who regularly attend college events, such as sporting events, concerts, or lectures, tend to have a higher sense of belonging to the college community. These students also report feeling more connected to other students and faculty. However, the study found that attending these events was not the sole reason for this sense of belonging. Students who had participated in extracurricular activities, such as clubs or volunteer organizations, also reported a higher sense of belonging to the college community. Therefore, the study’s findings suggest that ______',
