  stimulus_text = 'The writer''s main point is that the use of social media in the classroom, while potentially beneficial, requires careful consideration. The author suggests that teachers need to think critically about the ways in which social media can be used to support learning and to avoid using it in ways that might distract or disengage students. What is the most likely reason the writer includes the sentence "Teachers need to think critically about the ways in which social media can be used to support learning and to avoid using it in ways that might distract or disengage students?"',
